\id 2TI 2 TIM 56 Soli bible version
\h 2 Timoti
\toc1 Kalata ya cibili ya Paulo kuli Timoti
\toc2 2 Timoti
\toc3 2 Timoti
\mt2 Kalata ya cibili ya Paulo kuli
\mt1 Timoti
\imt1 BUSANSULUSHI
\ip Libuku lya Timoti wa cibili ni kalata yacibili ya mutumwa Paulo njalatuma kuli shikwiya Timoti. Libuku ili lya Timoti lyalalembwa cakumapwililisho a buyumi bwa Paulo. Pacindici walikuba wasungwa mu jele ku Loma. 1:16. Palikuba kunyumfwana kwaina pakati pali Paulo ne Timoti, kayi cindi conse walikumukuweti mwaname Bafilipi 2:22, 2 Timoti 1:12; 1:18,
\ip Kayi ni kalata ya makalata ana kufuma kuli Paulo alatumwa kubantu mumusena wakutuma ku mubungano. Makalata ambi atatu ni 1 Timoti, Tito ne Filimoni. Pacindi Paulo ncalikulemba Timoti wa cibili, baklistu bangi balikuba mu mapensho mu bwendeleshi bwa Ciloma, mpani ecebo cakendi Paulo ncalikubela mujele, ne kupa malailile Timoti kwambeti alimbikile mumakatasho. Mbuli mu Timoti wakutanguna, Paulo lamucenjeshenga Timoti sha beshikwiyisha bandemi shibili 1 Tim 1:16-18. Kayi lamwambilinga Timoti kwambeti kuntangu kulakesana cindi camakatasho. 2 Tim 3:1
\iot Mitwi ya makani
\io1 Cakutanguna Paulo lamupanga mitende Timoti 1:1-2
\io1 Kayi lamuyuminishinga Timoti kuba walimbikila 2:1-13
\io1 Cakonkapo lamupanga malailile angi 2:14-26
\io1 Lamucenjeshenga sha bintu byeshibikenshike kuntangu, kayi ne nshila yakwinshilamo 3:1 mpaka 4:8
\io1 Paulo lapwishinga ne kwambapo kwakendi pali Timoti.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Njame, Paulo mutumwa wa Klistu Yesu kwelana ne kuyanda kwa Lesa, walatumwa kuya kukambauka sha buyumi mbwalatushomesha mukwikatana ne Klistu Yesu.
\v 2 Ndalembelenga obe Timoti mwaname ngonsuni.
\p ndasengengeti luse, nkumbo kayi ne lumuno lwa Lesa Bata ne Klistu Yesu Mwami wetu, bibe pali njobe.
\s1 Lalumbaishinga Lesa ne kumuyuminisha Timoti
\p 
\v 3 Ndalumbunga Lesa ngondasebenselenga ne miyeyo yaswepa yabula mbuli bamashali bakame bakulukulu ncebalikwinsa. Ndalumbunga pakwinga nkandakulubunga mu mipailo yakame munshi ne mashiku sobwe.
\v 4 Ndanuka ncewalikulila misoshi, nkute kuyanda kwisa kukubona kwambeti nkakondwe ca makasa abili.
\v 5 Ndanuka lushomo lwa ncinencine ndobakute banyoko ba Yunisi ne bankambuyobe batukashi ba Loisi, ndashometi nenjobe elushomo ndokute.
\p 
\v 6 Neco ndakwanushungeti usheko mano kucipo ca Lesa ncokute ico ncewalatambula pasa mpondalabika makasa akame pali njobe ucisosele mulilo.
\v 7 Pakwinga Lesa liya kutupa Mushimu wa buyowa sobwe, Mushimu wa Lesa ukute kutupa ngofu, nelusuno kwambeti tucikonshenga kulitibuka.
\p 
\v 8 Neco kotanyumfwanga nsoni kuba kamboni wa Mwami Yesu, nambi kunyumfwa nsoni cebo ca kwambeti ame ndasungwa muno mu jele, obe libambile kucana mapensho, nomba Lesa nakakupe ngofu shakukambauka Mulumbe Waina.
\v 9 Walatupulusha ne kutukuwa kwambeti tube bantu bakendi, nkatwalikuba twelela kucitambula, nsombi bwalikuba bubambo ne nkumbo sha Lesa. nkumbo nshalatulesha kupitila mukwikatana ne Klistu Yesu kacitana cilengwa cindi.
\v 10 Lino Lesa walatuyubulwila ibi bintu mpwalaboneka Mupulushi wetu Klistu Yesu, nendi ewalapwisha ngofu sha lufu kupitila mu Mulumbe Waina, latwishibishi cena motwela kucanina buyumi butafu.
\p 
\v 11 Lesa walansala kwambeti mbe mukambaushi, mutumwa kayi shikwiyisha Mulumbe Waina.
\v 12 Encondapengelenga, ndiya nsoni pakwinga ndimwishi ngondashoma. Neco ndashometi wela kutabilisha cena bintu mbyabika mumakasa akame mpaka busuba bwashakabwele.
\v 13 Lino ikatisha camakasa abili maswi acancine ncine ngondalakwiyisha kwambeti, lushomo ne lusuno lwetu mukwikatana ne Klistu Yesu bibe cilesho kwakobe ca kukonkela.
\v 14 Kupitila muMushimu Uswepa ngotukute, ukunyamfwe kubamba cena buboni bwa palubasu mbowalapewa.
\p 
\v 15 Ucishi kwambeti bonse mu cimpansha ca Asiya balanshiya ndenka, pali abo balanshiya pali Figelo ne Hemojene.
\v 16 Nkumbo sha Lesa shibe mung'anda ya Onesifolo, pakwinga ewalikwisa kunjuminisha tunkanda twingi, kayi nkali kunyumfwa nsoni pakumbona kandi ndasungwa nshimbi mu jele.
\v 17 Mpwalesa ku Loma walanangaula mpaka walancana.
\v 18 Nkumbo sha Lesa shikabe pali Onesifolo pa busuba bwa lombolosho. Obe ucishi kufula kwa ncito shaina nshalikunyamfwa mpondalikuba ku Efenso.
\s1 Mushilikali wa Klistu
\c 2
\s1 Mushilikali wa Klistu
\p 
\v 1 Obe mwaname mulushomo, koyuminina mu nkumbo nshetukute mukwikatana ne Klistu Yesu.
\v 2 Konkela njiyishilo njowalanyumfwa ame kang'amba pa bakamboni bangi, nenjobe wiyisheko bantu beti bakacikonshe kwiyishako nabambi.
\p 
\v 3 Mantamo lubasu mu mapensho pakubeti mushilikali washomwa wa Klistu Yesu.
\v 4 Mushilikali nkakute kusha mano ku ncito shimbi, nsombi ukute kuyanda kukondwelesha mushilikali mukulene lamulangililinga.
\v 5 Nendi weshikufwamba lubilo lwa kufola mali nkabela kumufolesha na walilwa kukonkela milawo ya mfwambilo.
\v 6 kayi mulimi lasebensenga mwangofu ewela nanshi kulya bishango byakutanguna kutebula.
\v 7 Usheko mano ku makani ngondakwambili, Mwami Yesu nakakunyamfwe kwishiba bintu.
\p 
\v 8 Kwanukangeti, Yesu Klistu uyo walasemwa mu mukowa wa Dafeti, walapunduka kubafu mbuli ncolambanga Mulumbe Waina ngonkute kukambauka.
\v 9 Ndasungwa ncetani eti kapondo muno mu jele cebo ca kukambauka Mulumbe Waina, nomba necikabeco maswi a Lesa nkasungwa ncetani sobwe.
\v 10 Neco, nteti ntentuke cebo ca bantu mbwalasala Lesa kwambeti naboyo bakatambule lupulusho lwalesa kupitila muli Klistu Yesu kayi ne kutambula bulemu butapu.
\v 11 Makani awa nacancine ncine alambangeti;
\q1 Na twalafwila pamo nendi
\q1 nitukekale nebuyumi pamo nendiye.
\q1 
\v 12 Na tulimbikila
\q1 nitukendeleshe pamo.
\q1 Na tukamukane,
\q1 nendi nakatukane.
\q1 
\v 13 Na nkatwashomeka,
\q1 nendi nakabenga washomeka,
\q1 pakwinga nkela kulikana.
\s1 Musebenshi washomeka
\p 
\v 14 Kobanushanga bantu bintu ibi, ne kubacenjesha mwangofu pamenso a Lesa kwambeti kabatatotekeshananga pa maswi, nkacikute kunyamfwa sobwe. pakwinga cikute kunyonganya bantu balakutikinga.
\v 15 Elekesha mwangofu kuba wasuminishiwa pamenso a Lesa, eti musebenshi wabula nsoni; Ukute kwiyisha cena ancinencine.
\v 16 Talamuka ku mibandi yabuluya italete bulemu kuli Lesa, pakwinga ikute kubatalamusha kuli Lesa.
\v 17 Pakwinga mibandi ilico ilyeti cilonda cinene citashilikiki. Humenayo ne Fileto ebantu basuna mibandi ilico,
\v 18 balashiyi mukondo wancine ncine, balanyonganyango'wa lushomo lwa bantu, balambangeti bantu bafwa balapunduka kendi, kwamba kulico nteko kwa ncinencine sobwe.
\v 19 Nikukabeco, mpwaibaka Lesa nkapela kutenkanishiwa sobwe, pakwinga palembweti, “Mwami, ubeshi bantu bakendi” Kayi pali maswi akwambeti, “Muntu lakambilinga Mwami aleke kwinsa bintu byabula kululama.”
\p 
\v 20 Mung'anda inene mukute kuba mbale shapusana pusana, shagolide neshasilifa neshakubesa kayi ne shakubumba. Pa mbale ishi pali shakusebensesha cindi conse, nashimbi nishakubensesha pa cindi celela.
\v 21 Na muntu ucileka kwinsa byaipa, uliswepesha, ulyeti mbale shakusebensesha pa cindi celela, pakwinga nakabe waswepa kuli Mwami wakendi, kwambeti amusebenseshe cindi conse muncito yaina.
\v 22 Talamuka ku lunkumbwa lwa mubili. Obe konkela bululami, nelushomo, nelusuno kayi ne lumuno. Ikatana pamo ne bantu balakambililinga Mwami ne myoyo yaswepa.
\v 23 Kayi koleka kumantamo lubasu mu kutotekeshanya kwa buluya kwabula mano, ucisheti kukutowa kuleta kukangana.
\v 24 Musebenshi wa Mwami Lesa nkela kuba shikukangano'wa ne bantu, nsombi wela kunyumfwila nkumbo bantu bonse, shikwiyisha wekalikana cena moyo.
\v 25 Kolicepeshanga wambanga ne bantu balakutotekenga, mpani Lesa ngobapa cindi ca kusanduka kwambeti beshibe ca ncinencine mwalumbuluka.
\v 26 Mpani mano abo ngabwelelamo kwambeti bafume mu kose ka Satana wabekateti bensenga ncalayandanga.
\s1 Masuba amapwililisho
\c 3
\s1 Masuba a mapwililisho
\p 
\v 1 Ishibeti masuba akupwililisha nakabe amakatasho.
\v 2 Pakwinga nikukabe bantu balisuna, balunkumbwa lwa bubile, beshikulilumbaisha, beshikulisumpula, babula bulemu,bamatuka, batanyumfwili bamashali, batalumbu kayi batasakamana cendo cabo.
\v 3 Babula lusuno, batalekelele banabo, beshikubumba makani, batakonsho kulitibuka, bakalu, batasuni bintu byaina.
\v 4 Beshikulisha banabo, batasakamana ne buyumi, beshi kulitunta, kayi mu musena wa kusuna Lesa, balo nibakasunengo'wa bintu bishi kubakondwelesha.
\v 5 Beshi kuboneka kunsa eti balapailinga Lesa, kakuli balakananga ngofu yela kubashinta micito yabo yaipa, bantu balico ubatalamuke.
\v 6 Pakati pabo pali bantu bakute kwenda kashila mbali kuya mu manda abantu kuya kwikata busha batukashi baluya, balefuka balemenwa ne bwipishi kayi, bamantika ne lunkumbwa lwapusana pusana.
\v 7 Aba batukashi bakute kuyandishisha kwiya cindi conse, nsombi nkabakute kucana ca ncinencine sobwe.
\v 8 Mbuli Yanesi ne Yambule ncebalamutoteka Mose, aba naboyo balalwananga ne cancine ncine. Miyeyo yabo yafwa, lushomo lwabo ntelo lwa ncinencine.
\v 9 Nambi balenshingeco, paliya nkobalenga pakwinga buluya bwabo nibukaboneke kubantu bonse mbuli ncebwalaboneka buluya bwa Yambule ne Yanesi.
\s1 Maswi akulayana
\p 
\v 10 Lino obe wishicena ncenkute kwiyisha, wishi cena cendo cakame, ne miyeyo yakame, ne lushomo lwakame, ne kwikalikana moyo kwakame, ne lusuno lwakame, kayi ne kutatyompwa kwakame.
\v 11 Kayi waishi makatasho ne mapensho ngondalakumana nawo ku Antiyokeya, neku Ikoniya ne ku Lusitala. Ee, ndalapenga, nsombi Mwami walampulusha mu mapensho onsa'wo.
\v 12 Kayi ni cancinencine uliyense layandanga buyumi muli Yesu Klistu nibakamupenshe.
\v 13 Nomba bamicito yaipa ne bandemishibili nibakapitilishepo kwipa kubepa ne kubepwa.
\v 14 Nomba obe konkela mbyowaleishiwa ne kubishoma pakwinga ubeshi bantu balakwiyisha bintu ibi.
\v 15 Kufuma kubutwanike bwakobe uleshibi Mabala Aswepa ela kukupa mano akushoma muli Klistu Yesu kwambeti ukapuluke.
\v 16 Mabala Aswepa onse alafubailwa ne Lesa kayi alayandikinga pa kwiyisha, pakukansa bantu pa bilubo byabo, pa kululamika bintu ne kupa busele mubululami.
\v 17 Kwambeti muntu lasebenselenda Lesa abe wakwana cancinencine kwinsa ncito iliyonse yaina.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Pamenso a Lesa ne Klistu Yesu, uyo lakesanga kombolosha bayumi ne bafwa, pakwinga lakesanga kali Mwami, ndakwambilinga mwangofu ndeti,
\v 2 kambauka Mulumbe wa Lesa pa cindi bantu ncebalayandanga kukutika, ne pa cindi ncebatasuni kukutika. Balulamike nekubakalalila kayi ne kubayuminisha pakubeisha ca moyonteka.
\v 3 Cilakashikinga cindi nceti bakatatike kukana kwiyisha kwa ncine ncine, neco nibakayande beshikwiyisha bintu byelana ne mbyobalandanga kunyumfwa.
\v 4 Nibakakonkelengo'wa tulabi ne kukana kunyumfwa ca ncine ncine,
\v 5 obe kolilama mu bintu byonse, kotalefuka mumakatasho, sebensa ncito ya kukambauka Mulumbe Waina, kwanilisha ncito yakobe.
\p 
\v 6 Ame ndili pepi kufwa. Buyumi bwakame bulyeti mulumbo uletilwanga pa nteme.
\v 7 Ndalwana nkondo yaina, ndapwishi kufwamba lubilo kayi ndashomeke mpaka kumapwililisho.
\v 8 Pa cino cindi munshini wa bululami ulampembelelenga uwo Mwami Lesa momboloshi walulama ngoshakampe pa busuba busa, nomba nteti akapo'wa ame ndenka, nsombi nakape bonse balapembelelenga kwisa kwakendi.
\s1 Maswi a Paulo mwine
\p 
\v 9 Fwambana kwisa kuno,
\v 10 Dema layandishishi bintu bya mucishi lanshiyi waya ku Tesalonika. Kelesike waya ku Galatiya, neye Tito waya ku Dalamatiya,
\v 11 Kuno ndili ne Luka enka. Pakwisa ukese pamo ne Maliko kwambeti akese akanyamfweko ncito.
\v 12 Tukiko ndamutuma ku Efenso.
\v 13 Pakwisa ukandeteleleko munganjo ngondalashiya kuli Kalipo ku Tulowa, kayi ukaletelele asa mabuku akame abipaya.
\v 14 Alekisandulo shatwela usa walanjinshila bintu byaipa, nsombi Mwami Lesa nakamubweshele byaipa.
\v 15 Alekisandulo walikutoteka mulumbe ngotwali kukambauka, ne njobe ucenjele nendi.
\v 16 Mpondali kulitabilisha pakomboloshewa pa cindi cakutanguna paliya walanyamfwa, bonse balamwaika. Nomba Lesa katabapa mulandu sobwe.
\v 17 Nomba Lesa walikuba ne njame, walampa ngofu sha kukambauka mulumbe kwambeti bantu batamwishi Lesa, kayi ndalapuluka kulufu.
\v 18 Lesa nakamfune mu byaipa byonse ne kuntwala mu Bwami bwakendi bwa kwilu. Kulyendiye kube bulemu butapu! Ameni.
\s1 Maswi akulayana
\p 
\v 19 Umpeleko mitende Pulisika ne Akula ne ba mung'anda ya Onesifolo.
\v 20 Elasito washalila ku Kolinto, neye Tolofimo ndalamushiya kakolwa pa nsumbu ya Mileto.
\p 
\v 21 Ufwambane kwisa kuno kacitana cishika cindi ca mupewo.
\p Yubulu, ne Puludensi, ne Linosi ne Kolodiyasi kayi ne banse bonse bashoma muli Mwami Klistu balamupanga mitende.
\p 
\v 22 Mwami abe nenjobe kayi kwina moyo kwakendi Lesa kube nenjamwe.
